## 1. Executive Summary

### What We're Building
Three features extracted from analyzing Segwise.ai and Heyflow.ai — capabilities that fill real gaps in our existing platform without subscribing to either tool.

### Existing Platform Context
| Platform | URL | Tech Stack | Role |
|----------|-----|------------|------|
| Ad Campaign Engine (ACE) | adengine.insightprofit.live | React + Tailwind + Convex | Creative Factory, Campaign Ops, Data Intelligence |
| OfferEngine v3 | offers.insightprofit.live | React + Tailwind + Convex | Funnel builder, A/B testing, quiz funnels |
| UMDM | Supabase (self-hosted) | n8n + Supabase | Cross-channel marketing data model |
| Clarity CRO | GTM + Clarity | Microsoft Clarity | Session recordings, heatmaps, behavioral analytics |
| Customer Avatar Registry | Internal JSON registry | JSON + scripts | 294+ avatars across 5 brands, 12 personality frameworks |

### Three Features to Build

| # | Feature | Target Platform | Inspired By | Priority |
|---|---------|----------------|-------------|----------|
| 1 | Creative Intelligence Module | Ad Campaign Engine | Segwise.ai | HIGH |
| 2 | Phone Validation + SMS OTP | OfferEngine v3 | Heyflow.ai | MEDIUM |
| 3 | Competitor Ad Monitoring | Ad Campaign Engine | Segwise.ai | MEDIUM |

