## 2. Feature 1: Creative Intelligence Module

### 2.1 Problem Statement
Our Ad Campaign Engine currently scores creatives at the **format/concept level** (e.g., "video ads outperform image ads"). We lack **element-level creative intelligence** — understanding which specific hook dialogue, CTA phrasing, color palette, character emotion, or audio cue drives ROAS. This is the core capability Segwise.ai sells for $250-5,000+/mo.

### 2.2 What We're Building
An AI-powered Creative Intelligence Module that automatically decomposes every ad creative into tagged elements, maps those elements to performance metrics, and surfaces actionable insights about what specific creative elements drive results.

### 2.3 Architecture Overview

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    CREATIVE INTELLIGENCE MODULE (CIM)                             │
│                    Segwise-Equivalent • Zero SaaS Cost                            │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                                  │
│  ┌─────────────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────────┐  ┌───────────────────┐   │
│  │  AI CREATIVE TAGGER     │  │  TAG-METRIC MAPPER   │  │  INSIGHT ENGINE   │   │
│  │                         │  │                      │  │                   │   │
│  │  • GPT-4o Vision API    │  │  • Tag → ROAS        │  │  • Top Elements   │   │
│  │  • Video frame extract  │  │  • Tag → CPA         │  │  • Fatigue Alerts │   │
│  │  • Audio transcription  │  │  • Tag → CTR         │  │  • Recommendations│   │
│  │  • Text/copy extraction │  │  • Tag → Conv Rate   │  │  • Creative Brief │   │
│  │  • Auto-categorization  │  │  • Tag → LTV         │  │  • Kill/Scale     │   │
│  └────────────┬────────────┘  └──────────┬───────────┘  └─────────┬─────────┘   │
│               │                          │                        │              │
│               └──────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┘              │
│                                          ▼                                       │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│
│  │                     SUPABASE — creative_intelligence_* tables               ││
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│
│                                          │                                       │
│                                          ▼                                       │
│  ┌──────────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│  │  ACE DASHBOARD WIDGET    │  │  UMDM PERFORMANCE DATA (existing tables)    │  │
│  │  (new React page)        │  │  umdm_ads + umdm_metrics_daily             │  │
