| Component | Per-Unit Cost | Monthly Estimate |
|-----------|-------------|-----------------|
| Twilio Lookup (carrier check) | $0.005/lookup | 500 leads × $0.005 = $2.50/mo |
| Twilio Verify (OTP) | $0.05/verification | 500 leads × $0.05 = $25.00/mo |
| **Total** | | **~$27.50/mo** at 500 leads/mo |

