## 6. Acceptance Criteria & QA Checklist

### Feature 1: Creative Intelligence Module

| # | Criteria | Test |
|---|---------|------|
| 1.1 | Image creatives are automatically tagged with ≥15 tags each | Upload 5 sample images, verify ≥15 tags per image |
| 1.2 | Video creatives extract keyframes + audio transcription | Upload 3 sample videos, verify frame-level + audio tags |
| 1.3 | Tag performance aggregation produces correct ROAS/CPA per tag | Seed 50 creatives with known metrics, verify aggregation math |
| 1.4 | Fatigue detection fires alerts at correct thresholds | Seed declining-performance creative data, verify alert generation |
| 1.5 | Dashboard renders tag heatmap with click-to-drill-down | Manual UI verification |
| 1.6 | Creative deep dive page shows all tags + performance timeline | Manual UI verification |
| 1.7 | Tag explorer search/filter works correctly | Search by category, verify results |
| 1.8 | Integration: UMDM data flows into CIM correctly | Verify join between cim_creative_assets and umdm_metrics_daily |
| 1.9 | All cron jobs run successfully on schedule | Verify cron execution logs for 48 hours |
| 1.10 | API endpoints return correct data with proper pagination | Test all 9 endpoints with various filters |

### Feature 2: Phone Validation + SMS OTP

| # | Criteria | Test |
|---|---------|------|
| 2.1 | Phone validation correctly identifies mobile/VoIP/landline | Test with 5 known mobile, 3 VoIP, 2 landline numbers |
| 2.2 | VoIP blocking works when enabled | Enable blockVoip, test with Google Voice number |
| 2.3 | OTP SMS is sent within 5 seconds of request | Test with real phone, measure delivery time |
| 2.4 | OTP verification accepts correct 6-digit code | Test with correct code |
| 2.5 | OTP verification rejects incorrect code and counts attempts | Test with wrong codes, verify 3-attempt limit |
| 2.6 | Lead quality scoring produces correct grades | Seed 10 test leads with known behaviors, verify scores |
| 2.7 | Funnel builder settings UI correctly configures validation | Toggle all settings, verify they persist and apply |
| 2.8 | Phone input component shows real-time validation feedback | Test UI with valid/invalid numbers |
| 2.9 | OTP modal auto-advances digits, handles resend, shows timer | Full UI walkthrough |
| 2.10 | Lead quality dashboard shows correct distribution | Seed 50 leads, verify donut chart + table |
| 2.11 | Country restrictions work (allow/block lists) | Test with US, UK, and blocked country numbers |
| 2.12 | WhatsApp channel works for OTP delivery | Test with WhatsApp-enabled number |

### Feature 3: Competitor Ad Monitoring

| # | Criteria | Test |
|---|---------|------|
| 3.1 | Meta Ad Library API returns competitor ads correctly | Add 2 known competitors, verify ads are pulled |
| 3.2 | New ads are detected and stored with first_seen_at | Check for new ad detection after 24h |
| 3.3 | Inactive ads are correctly marked | Verify ads that disappear from API are marked inactive |
| 3.4 | Competitor ads are tagged using same taxonomy as CIM | Verify tags on 10 competitor ads |
| 3.5 | Weekly trend report generates with valid insights | Verify report content after 1 week of data collection |
| 3.6 | Gap analysis correctly identifies opportunities | Seed our tags + competitor tags, verify gap detection |
| 3.7 | Competitor monitor dashboard renders all competitor cards | Manual UI verification |
| 3.8 | Competitor detail page shows ad gallery + tag cloud | Manual UI verification |
| 3.9 | Trend report page renders formatted insights | Manual UI verification |
| 3.10 | Slack notifications fire correctly for new campaigns | Verify Slack message on new competitor ad detection |
| 3.11 | Add Competitor flow works end-to-end | Add new competitor via UI, verify first data pull |

