## 7. Rollout Plan

### Phase 1: Foundation (Week 1-2)
- Set up all database tables (Supabase migration + Convex schema update)
- Implement GPT-4o Vision tagging pipeline (shared by Feature 1 + 3)
- Build phone validation backend (Twilio integration)
- Create API endpoints for all three features

### Phase 2: Feature 1 — Creative Intelligence (Week 2-3)
- Build asset ingestion pipeline + UMDM integration
- Implement tag performance aggregation cron
- Build fatigue detection algorithm + alerting
- Build 3 dashboard pages (Creative Intelligence, Deep Dive, Tag Explorer)

### Phase 3: Feature 2 — Phone Validation (Week 3)
- Build phone input component + OTP modal
- Build funnel builder settings panel
- Build lead quality scoring engine
- Add lead quality dashboard widget to OfferEngine

### Phase 4: Feature 3 — Competitor Monitoring (Week 3-4)
- Build Meta Ad Library API collector
- Build TikTok/Google scraping collectors
- Build weekly trend report generator
- Build 3 dashboard pages (Competitor Monitor, Detail, Trends)
- Seed initial 10 competitors

### Phase 5: Integration & QA (Week 4-5)
- End-to-end integration testing
- Full QA checklist execution (all 33 criteria above)
- Performance testing (ensure crons complete within timeouts)
- Slack notification testing
- User acceptance testing with @rmreal

### Phase 6: Launch (Week 5)
- Deploy to production
- Enable all crons
- Monitor for 48 hours
- Handoff documentation

